  "id": "RAW_84d2e1bb",
  "title": "百万 Token 也能无损压缩？C3 模型用“级联压缩”重新定义长上下文挑战",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247825918&idx=2&sn=e6b9cb9e604663db748ffabceac9a081",
  "date": "2025-12-12 13:05:00",
  "author": "CSDN",
  "siteName": "CSDN",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-mpa-category=\"正文\" data-mpa-template-id=\"1440\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <div style=\"padding:10px;max-width:100%;text-decoration:inherit;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(240, 242, 246);font-family:inherit;border-style:solid;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:5px 16px;max-width:100%;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">【编者按】</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 15px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">百万级别 Token 的输入，正在成为大型语言模型（LLMs）长上下文任务中的计算与内存“噩梦”。DeepSeekOCR 凭借“上下文光学压缩”技术实现了 10 倍 Token 压缩率，引发全网热议。但透过现象看本质，高压缩率的秘密，真的在于“图像化”吗？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 | 刘帆帆</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">出品丨作者投稿</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">DeepSeekOCR 的成功让许多人误以为“视觉编码”是压缩的关键。然而，研究团队经过深入分析发现，高压缩率的核心其实源自 Latent Tokens（潜在 Token）本身——这是一种比离散文本 Token 更高效、密度更高的信息载体。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">基于这一洞察，作者所在的研究团队提出了一种直击本质的全新路径：Context&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Cascade Compression (C3，上下文级联压缩)。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">将两种路径进行对比：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">DeepSeek OCR 路径： 文本 → 图像 → 视觉 Token → 语言模型（引入了布局、噪点、视觉编码器等无关干扰）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">C3 路径： 文本 → 文本 Latent Tokens → 语言模型（纯粹、无损、直接）</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">具体来说，一个小型 LLM 作为第一级，通过将长上下文压缩成一组潜在 token（例如，长度为 32 或 64），实现高比例的文本 token 到潜在 token 的压缩。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">一个大型 LLM 作为第二级，然后对这个压缩的上下文执行解码任务。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这一设计也验证了近期热门论文《LANGUAGE MODELS ARE INJECTIVE AND HENCE INVERTIBLE》中关于「LLM 本质是无损压缩」的论断。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">实验表明，在 20 倍压缩比（文本 token 数量是潜在 token 数量的 20 倍）下，C3 实现了 98% 的解码准确率，而 DeepSeek OCR 大约为60%。当我们进一步将压缩比增加到 40 倍时，准确率仍保持在约 93%。这表明在上下文压缩领域，C3 压缩比光学字符压缩展示了更优越的性能和可行性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">目前模型与代码现已开源：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">原文：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2511.15244\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2511.15244</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">代码：<a href=\"https://github.com/liufanfanlff/C3-Context-Cascade-Compression\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/liufanfanlff/C3-Context-Cascade-Compression</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">模型：<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/liufanfanlff/C3-Context-Cascade-Compression\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/liufanfanlff/C3-Context-Cascade-Compression</a></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252192\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2c5b48b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QuwjkSP1G6wEJHaJCLTONqlcQexqRgJcIICxofIOJs6B6tWBfibb7now%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">架构</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在介绍 C3 之前，先带大家来了解一下 DeepSeek-OCR 的工作原理。DeepSeek-OCR 采用了一种创新的\"视觉压缩\"思路，这种方法的优势在于利用了视觉编码器强大的特征提取能力，但也面临着图像布局复杂性、低分辨率下的模糊等固有限制。C3 提出了一个更直接的压缩思路：跳过视觉中介，没有中间商赚差价，直接在文本域进行压缩。其核心架构包括：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1.双 LLM 级联设计</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小型 LLM（算力消耗低）作为压缩编码器，压缩上下文信息。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大型 LLM（推理生成能力强）作为解码器执行下游任务。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2.压缩机制</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">引入可学习的\"上下文查询\"（Context Query）嵌入</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将长文本压缩为固定长度的潜在token（如32或64个）。</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">完全保留预训练 LLM 的语言压缩能力</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100104842\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6407407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 394px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7a22889&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FVeJKXItpwPWib9PEu1NjqNcpAEMFEib7BibIcCR7VembyYTmYq7OhPX8W1ibEg0ZYCA4CXOhVgBqgASCzWuxGABQ1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252191\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c0d6be04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QDyP5HTUOXsPlJWd79yygiasaqXicpN7ibIfqiak5WFpaxE1mGxxpfmMjiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">性能表现</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 Fox 基准测试中，C3 展现出显著优势： &nbsp;</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在约 20 倍压缩时，C3 保持 98.4% 精度，而D eepSeek-OCR 降至59.1%</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即使在极限的 40 倍压缩率下（32 个潜在 token），C3 仍能维持 93% 以上的重建精度</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">独特的\"遗忘模式\"：更接近人类记忆</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100104843\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24259259259259258\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 438px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f4a63aa0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FVeJKXItpwPWib9PEu1NjqNcpAEMFEib7Bibo1iaicZDkibVvaCpAw5esNOWV6XkeZiaiboH4OwaGhPD81R8QIDicUy1uIbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D4\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究还发现了 C3 的一个有趣特性：当压缩率过高导致信息损失时，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">错误往往集中在文本末尾，呈现序列性信息衰减</span>。这与光学压缩方法的\"全局模糊\"不同，反而更类似人类记忆的渐进式遗忘过程。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这种特性使得 C3 在实际应用中更具可预测性——重要信息可以优先放置在文本前部，确保关键内容的完整保留。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">测试</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100104844\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"720\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=96dbd4a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FVeJKXItpwPWib9PEu1NjqNcpAEMFEib7Bib8MmfYdQiavw8uXibogLNV94NocTUW61uhEHQGK6qGiaMWxic05PvJph8hw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">无论是在长英文文本还是中文古文上均做到了近乎完美的压缩还原</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">甚至对于 LLM 一直难以处理的乱序文本也能精准还原</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100252190\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c02173a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q0QtgZAx8xsoTReptvArfwbn9MvHGVfV98Qkl5PMRS6MCt2ljwLJwoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">应用前景</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1. 超长上下文处理：C3 可作为现有 LLM 的\"前端压缩器\"，将百万级 token 的输入（如整本书籍、大型代码库）压缩到可处理范围，降低计算成本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2. 多模态：级连轻量级 VLM 和 LLM，轻量级 VLM 作为视觉 encoder 进行信息压缩，处理视觉信息丰富的长文档等。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3. 下一代模型的基础组件 ：C3 的编码-解码架构可直接应用于扩散语言模型和潜在自回归模型，将可变长度文本转换为固定长度潜在表示。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这是一个在有限的人力、算力与数据背景下诞生的“小而美”项目。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前 C3 的代码与权重开源，希望开源社区的研究者们能接过这一棒，激发出C3 的巨大潜能。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "C3 模型提出“上下文级联压缩”技术，通过小型 LLM 将长文本压缩为潜在 Token，再由大型 LLM 处理，实现了对百万级文本的无损高效压缩，相比视觉压缩表现更优。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "C3 模型提出“上下文级联压缩”技术，通过小型 LLM 将长文本压缩为潜在 Token，再由大型 LLM 处理，实现了对百万级文本的无损高效压缩，相比视觉压缩表现更优。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了一种名为 C3（Context Cascade Compression）的全新长上下文压缩技术，旨在解决大型语言模型在处理百万级 Token 输入时面临的计算与内存挑战。C3 的核心在于其“双 LLM 级联设计”：首先，一个小型 LLM 作为编码器，将长文本转化为固定长度的潜在 Token；随后，一个大型 LLM 作为解码器处理这些压缩后的信息。与 DeepSeek OCR 的视觉压缩路径不同，C3 直接在文本域进行压缩，避免了文本转化为图像再视觉编码，从而消除了布局、噪点等视觉编码引入的无关干扰，路径更为纯粹、无损。实验结果显示，C3 在 20 倍压缩比下达到了 98%的解码准确率，远超 DeepSeek OCR 的约 60%；即使在 40 倍压缩比下，准确率仍能保持 93%以上。C3 还展现出类似人类记忆的“遗忘模式”，即信息损失集中在文本末尾，这有利于关键信息的优先保留。该技术已被开源，具有超长上下文处理、多模态应用及作为下一代模型基础组件的广阔前景。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "C3 模型通过纯文本域的“级联压缩”实现长上下文高效处理，其原理优于视觉压缩。",
